    <div class="body">
        <p>Hi there,
All View Helpers with option attribute renders reversed options ($val=&gt;$key):
FormMultiCheckbox , FormSelect, FormRadio</p>

<p>ex:</p>

<pre class="highlight"><code>
$id_sexe = new Element('id_sexe');
$id_sexe-&gt;setAttributes(array(
'type' =&gt; 'radio'
'label' =&gt; 'gender',
'options' =&gt; array(1=&gt;'man',2=&gt;'woman') 
));
</code></pre>

<p>generates options like this: 12</p>

